            <td><em>Note controller</em><br /><span>0 - Display note</span><br /><span>1 - Do not display note</span><br /><br /></td>
            <td><em>Display constant controller</em><br /><span># - Related item</span><br /><span>8 - No display constant generated</span><br /><br /></td>
