                  <li>$b - Edition (NR)</li>
                  <li>$c - Qualifying information (NR)</li>
                  <li>$d - Place, publisher, and date of publication (NR)</li>
                  <li>$g - Related parts (R)</li>
                  <li>$h - Physical description (NR)</li>
                  <li>$i - Relationship information (R)</li>
                  <li>$k - Series data for related item (R)</li>
                  <li>$m - Material-specific details (NR)</li>
                  <li>$n - Note (R)</li>
                  <li>$o - Other item identifier (R)</li>
                  <li>$r - Report number (R)</li>
                  <li>$s - Uniform title (NR)</li>
